[09/05/2019 16:57:45] <font color="#ffffff">Esta isla apartada</font>
[09/05/2019 16:57:45] <font color="#ffffff">en el Iago de Last Mountain,</font>
[09/05/2019 16:57:49] <font color="#ffffff">en Saskatchewan Central,</font>
[09/05/2019 16:57:49] <font color="#ffffff">es el territorio de cría perfecto.</font>
[09/05/2019 16:57:57] <font color="#ffffff">Aunque han pasado</font>
